metadata.name: GHÖETIKA •NESSA•
metadata.description:
•NESSA• By Facy Sedated
4000x4000 


Nessa is a girl who has lived her entire life without having a true home, since her life began she was rejected and despised, she has had to fight since she breathed for the first time, although nothing has been easy for her, that has not prevented her from enjoying From the smallest details around her, she has always loved observing people's gestures and trying to decipher what they feel, she believes that understanding and empathizing with the emotions of another could help her understand and control her emotions.
